    DatasetCatalogue
    A catalogue of Datasets and the default plotting information for the Variables contained within them

    Interface defining the enahnced metadata about a variable, including title, description, copyright/more info and default values for layer plotting Any of these methods may return null if no default is set.

    An interface defining a catalogue which can extract DiscreteFeatures based on a String identifier and a set of PlottingDomainParams

    StyleCatalogue
    A catalogue of supported styles for plotting.
